Attendify AI

Visit Attendify AI
attendifyai.netlify.app

Attendify AI is an advanced facial recognition attendance system that streamlines attendance management through artificial intelligence. It leverages cutting-edge computer vision techniques to accurately recognize faces and record attendance with minimal human intervention.

Features

Face Registration: Register faces with personal information (name, roll number, SRN number).

Attendance Marking: Automated attendance through facial recognition.

Real-Time Processing: Quickly detects and marks attendance.

Data Storage: Uses SQL for structured and reliable data management.

Modern UI: Clean and responsive design, compatible with various devices.

Webcam Integration: Direct webcam access for attendance marking.

Technologies Used

Backend: Flask (Python)

Frontend: React.js

Database: SQL

Face Recognition: dlib and OpenCV

Installation

Clone the repository:

git clone https://github.com/username/attendify-ai.git
cd attendify-ai

Install backend dependencies:

pip install -r backend/requirements.txt

Set up the frontend:

cd frontend
npm install
npm start

Run the backend server:

cd backend
flask run

Usage

Register new students by uploading their photos.

Access the attendance dashboard.

Use the "Mark Attendance" feature to open the webcam and record attendance.

